    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo"><a href="#hexo" class="headerlink" title="hexo"></a>hexo</h1><h3 id="安装-node-js"><a href="#安装-node-js" class="headerlink" title="安装 node.js"></a>安装 node.js</h3><p>这个不用说了，常常使用 node.js， 环境肯定是必要的。</p><p><img src="/2022/09/16/hexo/nodejs.png" alt="image-20220916101935683"></p><p>安装完之后会有两个东西，一个是 <code>nodejs</code> 本身，一个是 <code>npm</code> 包管理器。</p><figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autohotkey">❯ node -v<br>v16.<span class="hljs-number">16.0</span><br>❯ npm -v<br>npm WARN config global `--global`, `--local` are deprecated. Use `--location=global` instead.<br><span class="hljs-number">8.18</span>.<span class="hljs-number">0</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装-hexo"><a href="#安装-hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo"></a>安装 hexo</h3><p>由于 <code>nodejs</code> 的服务器在国外，在国内安装下载会很慢，我们可以使用 <code>nrm</code> 工具来切换镜像源。 </p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">❯ nrm ls<br><br>  npm ---------- https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>registry.npmjs.org/<br>  yarn --------- https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>registry.yarnpkg.com/<br>  tencent ------ https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//mi</span>rrors.cloud.tencent.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/npm/</span><br>  cnpm --------- https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>r.cnpmjs.org/<br>* taobao ------- https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>registry.npmmirror.com/<br>  npmMirror ---- https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>skimdb.npmjs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/registry/</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>现在所使用的就是 <code>taobao</code> 镜像源。</p><p>安装 hexo</p><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql">❯ npm install hexo-cli -g<br>npm WARN config <span class="hljs-keyword">global</span> `<span class="hljs-comment">--global`, `--local` are deprecated. Use `--location=global` instead.</span><br><br>added <span class="hljs-number">59</span> packages <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span>s<br>npm <span class="hljs-keyword">notice</span><br>npm <span class="hljs-keyword">notice</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">New</span> minor <span class="hljs-keyword">version</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">of</span> npm available! <span class="hljs-number">8.18</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span> -&gt; <span class="hljs-number">8.19</span><span class="hljs-number">.2</span><br>npm <span class="hljs-keyword">notice</span> Changelog: https://github.com/npm/cli/releases/tag/v8<span class="hljs-number">.19</span><span class="hljs-number">.2</span><br>npm <span class="hljs-keyword">notice</span> Run npm install -g npm@<span class="hljs-number">8.19</span><span class="hljs-number">.2</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">to</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">update</span>!<br>npm <span class="hljs-keyword">notice</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以验证一下是否安装成功</p><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm">❯ hexo -v<br>hexo-<span class="hljs-keyword">cli</span>: <span class="hljs-number">4.3</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">os:</span> win32 <span class="hljs-number">10.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.19043</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">node:</span> <span class="hljs-number">16.16</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">v8:</span> <span class="hljs-number">9.4</span><span class="hljs-number">.146</span><span class="hljs-number">.24</span>-node<span class="hljs-number">.21</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">uv:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1.43</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">zlib:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1.2</span><span class="hljs-number">.11</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">brotli:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.9</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">ares:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1.18</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">modules:</span> <span class="hljs-number">93</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">nghttp2:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1.47</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">napi:</span> <span class="hljs-number">8</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">llhttp:</span> <span class="hljs-number">6.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.7</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">openssl:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1.1</span><span class="hljs-number">.1</span>q+quic<br><span class="hljs-symbol">cldr:</span> <span class="hljs-number">40.0</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">icu:</span> <span class="hljs-number">70.1</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">tz:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2021</span>a3<br><span class="hljs-symbol">unicode:</span> <span class="hljs-number">14.0</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">ngtcp2:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0.1</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span>-DEV<br><span class="hljs-symbol">nghttp3:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0.1</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span>-DEV<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="创建根目录"><a href="#创建根目录" class="headerlink" title="创建根目录"></a>创建根目录</h3><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc">❯ cd /<br>❯ md hexo<br><br><span class="hljs-code">    Directory: C:\</span><br><br>Mode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name<br><span class="hljs-bullet">----                 </span>-------------         ------ ----<br>d----           2022/9/16    10:29                hexo<br>❯ cd .\hexo\<br>❯ ls<br>❯ pwd<br><br><span class="hljs-section">Path</span><br><span class="hljs-section">----</span><br>C:\hexo<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果搭建的过程中有问题，可以将这个文件夹干掉重新来过就行了，不用畏惧。</p><h3 id="建站"><a href="#建站" class="headerlink" title="建站"></a>建站</h3><figure class="highlight vhdl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs vhdl">❯ hexo init<br>INFO  Cloning hexo-starter https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-starter.git<br>INFO  Install dependencies<br><span class="hljs-literal">warning</span> hexo-renderer-stylus &gt; stylus &gt; css &gt; source-<span class="hljs-keyword">map</span>-resolve@<span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>.<span class="hljs-number">0</span>: See https://github.com/lydell/source-<span class="hljs-keyword">map</span>-resolve#deprecated<br><span class="hljs-literal">warning</span> Your current version <span class="hljs-keyword">of</span> Yarn <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">out</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">of</span> date. The latest version <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;1.22.19&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> you<span class="hljs-symbol">&#x27;re</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">on</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;1.22.18&quot;</span>.<br>INFO  Start blogging <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> Hexo!<br>❯ ls<br>.github<br>node_modules<br>scaffolds<br>source<br>themes<br>_config.landscape.yml<br>_config.yml<br>.gitignore<br><span class="hljs-keyword">package</span>.json<br>yarn.lock<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="启动"><a href="#启动" class="headerlink" title="启动"></a>启动</h3><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql">❯ hexo s<br><span class="hljs-keyword">INFO</span>  Validating config<br><span class="hljs-keyword">INFO</span>  <span class="hljs-keyword">Start</span> processing<br><span class="hljs-keyword">INFO</span>  Hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> running at http://localhost:<span class="hljs-number">4000</span>/ . Press Ctrl+C <span class="hljs-keyword">to</span> stop.<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个时候博客已经有了，而且默认创建了一篇文章，就叫做 <code>hello world</code> 。</p><p><img src="/2022/09/16/hexo/helloworld.png" alt="image-20220916103900781"></p><h3 id="新建文章"><a href="#新建文章" class="headerlink" title="新建文章"></a>新建文章</h3><p>使用 <code>Ctrl + C</code>，终止。</p><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql">❯ hexo s<br><span class="hljs-keyword">INFO</span>  Validating config<br><span class="hljs-keyword">INFO</span>  <span class="hljs-keyword">Start</span> processing<br><span class="hljs-keyword">INFO</span>  Hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> running at http://localhost:<span class="hljs-number">4000</span>/ . Press Ctrl+C <span class="hljs-keyword">to</span> stop.<br><span class="hljs-keyword">INFO</span>  Farewell<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;<code>hexo s</code> 这个启动命令平时就是做预览用。&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><p>我们生成文章方式有两种，一种是通过命令行的方式，一种是通过直接在相应的路径下创建文件。</p><p>命令行方式</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">❯ hexo n <span class="hljs-string">&quot;test&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Validating<span class="hljs-built_in"> config</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in"></span><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Created: C:\hexo\source\_posts\test.md<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>直接创建文件</p><p>直接在 <code>C:\hexo\source\_posts\</code> 路径下创建 <code>md</code> 文件也可以。这个自己测试一下就行了。</p><p>这时候博客的搭建就已经完成了。</p><h3 id="部署到-gitee"><a href="#部署到-gitee" class="headerlink" title="部署到 gitee"></a>部署到 <code>gitee</code></h3><p>博客不可能就只放到本地用，我们需要把它部署到远端去。一种免费的方式就是部署到 <code>gitee</code> 上面去。</p><p>创建仓库。</p><p>开启 <code>gitpages</code> 服务。</p><p><img src="/2022/09/16/hexo/gitpagesone.png" alt="image-20220916111553832"></p><p><img src="/2022/09/16/hexo/gitpagestwo.png" alt="image-20220916111601126"></p><p>等待审核，听说是巨慢，要等一两天。</p><h3 id="尝试-github"><a href="#尝试-github" class="headerlink" title="尝试 github"></a>尝试 github</h3><p><img src="/2022/09/16/hexo/github.png" alt="image-20220916112101236"></p><h3 id="安装-git-部署插件"><a href="#安装-git-部署插件" class="headerlink" title="安装 git 部署插件"></a>安装 git 部署插件</h3><figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autohotkey">❯ npm install --save hexo-deployer-git<br>npm WARN config global `--global`, `--local` are deprecated. Use `--location=global` instead.<br><br>added <span class="hljs-number">1</span> package, <span class="hljs-literal">and</span> changed <span class="hljs-number">19</span> packages in <span class="hljs-number">2</span>s<br><br><span class="hljs-number">19</span> packages are looking for funding<br>  run `npm fund` for details<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="设置-config-yml"><a href="#设置-config-yml" class="headerlink" title="设置 _config.yml"></a>设置 <code>_config.yml</code></h3><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-meta"># Deployment</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">## Docs: https:<span class="hljs-comment">//hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">deploy:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  type:</span> git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  repo:</span> git@github.com:liusuboop/liusuboop.github.io.git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  branch:</span> master<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="部署到远端"><a href="#部署到远端" class="headerlink" title="部署到远端"></a>部署到远端</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br></pre></t